LINUX SYSTEM ADMINISTRATION

Step 1: Ensure/Double Check Permissions on Sensitive Files
1. ls -l shadow 
   sudo chmod g-r shadow
2. ls -l gshadow
   sudo chmod g-r gshadow
3. ls -l group 
   sudo chmod 644 group 
4. ls -l passwd 
   sudo chmod 644 passwd 

Step 2: Create User Accounts
1. sudo adduser admin
   sudo adduser sam
   sudo adduser joe 
   sudo adduser amy 
   sudo adduser sara
2. sudo usermod -aG sudo admin

Step 3: Create User Group and Collaborative Folder
1. sudo addgroup engineers 
2. sudo usermod -G engineers sam
   sudo usermod -G engineers joe 
   sudo usermod -G engineers amy
   sudo usermod -G engineers sara
3. sudo mkdir  /home/engineers
4. sudo chown :engineers /home/engineers

Step 4: Lynis Auditing
1. sudo apt install lynis 
2. sudo lynis --help 
3. sudo lynis audit system
